---
title: Easy Beyond Meat® Cottage Pie with Cheesy Cheddar Mashed Potatoes
description: This classic casserole combines saucy Beyond Meat® filling with extra cheesy cheddar mashed potatoes. Broiling for the last few minutes gives this cottage pie a delicious golden crust.

